name: MarineChimairamon
description: MarineChimairamon is a chimera of various Digimon. It has the head and legs of Coelamon , the horn, tusks, ears and mane of Ikkakumon , the horns of Octomon as well as its tentacles for a tail, the body of Seadramon , the dorsal fins of Dolphmon , the tentacles of Gesomon on its back, the left arm of Ebidramon , and the right arm of Divermon holding the Trent.
